n that which he knew not.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["when","where","who"],"pos":"N","lemma":"ما","tier":"q100","transliteration":"mā"},{"id":"ac-96:5:5","surahNum":96,"ayahNum":5,"wordNum":5,"arabic":"عَلِمَ","targetTranslation":"he knows/learns (in the phrase 'what he did not know')","ayahArabic":"عَلَّمَ ٱلْإِنسٰنَ مَا لَمْ يَعْلَمْ","ayahEnglish":"Taught man that which he knew not.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["he feared","he judged","he created"],"pos":"V","lemma":"عَلِمَ","tier":"q100","transliteration":"yaʿlam"},{"id":"ac-96:7:2","surahNum":96,"ayahNum":7,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"رَأَى","targetTranslation":"he saw him (connected to أَن before it)","ayahArabic":"أَن رَّءَاهُ ٱسْتَغْنَىٰٓ","ayahEnglish":"Because he sees himself self-sufficient.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["judged","created","disbelieved"],"pos":"V","lemma":"رَأَى","tier":"q100","transliteration":"raāhu"},{"id":"ac-96:7:3","surahNum":96,"ayahNum":7,"wordNum":3,"arabic":"اسْتَغْنَى","targetTranslation":"he considered himself free from need (because رَّءَاهُ - he saw himself)","ayahArabic":"أَن رَّءَاهُ ٱسْتَغْنَىٰٓ","ayahEnglish":"Because he sees himself self-sufficient.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["and those who","But if","and We will leave"],"pos":"V","lemma":"اسْتَغْنَى","tier":"q_all","transliteration":"is'taghnā"},{"id":"ac-96:8:3","surahNum":96,"ayahNum":8,"wordNum":3,"arabic":"رَبّ","targetTranslation":"your Lord (owned, after إِلَىٰ)","ayahArabic":"إِنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ ٱلرُّجْعَىٰٓ","ayahEnglish":"Indeed, to your Lord is the return.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["A warning","A balance","A path"],"pos":"N","lemma":"رَبّ","tier":"q100","transliteration":"rabbika"},{"id":"ac-96:9:1","surahNum":96,"ayahNum":9,"wordNum":1,"arabic":"أ","targetTranslation":"have you seen/considered? (asking about ٱلَّذِى يَنْهَىٰ - the one who forbids)","ayahArabic":"أَرَءَيْتَ ٱلَّذِى يَنْهَىٰ","ayahEnglish":"Have you seen the one who forbids","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["com